Introduction

Kim Jae-hyun, also known as Jaehyeon, is a South Korean idol trainee under C-JeS Entertainment. He is a member of the boy group WHIB, debuting on November 8, 2023.

Before training to become an idol, Jaehyeon was a competitive figure skater from 2011-2019.
